rows.label: xs33600100_MSG0010
rows.name:
Well, well, what a surprise.
Fancy meeting you here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33600100_MSG0020
rows.name: ...Kidding. I knew you'd be along any minute now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33600100_MSG0040
rows.name:
No paycheck at the end of this one.
Best to get it over and done with.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33600100_MSG0050
rows.name:
I'm feelin' pretty tense.
Might have to go off the chain shortly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33600100_MSG0060
rows.name: You too. You better keep up, or else.[ST:wait ]
